title: Bobby's Dancing With The Stars Partner Stops By & Answer Show's Questions
itunes:title: Bobby's Dancing With The Stars Partner Stops By & Answer Show's Questions
description:
Bobby's DWTS partner Sharna Burgess stops by and talks about what it has been like working with Bobby so far. Also, Jon Pardi drops by to talk about his latest single "Night Shift."
